            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
### Fixed
- The app now launches reliably from the packaged build. SwiftPM resource
  bundles are resolved from the app's `Contents/Resources`, fixing a startup
  failure where the previous build could fail to load its bundled resources.
